<HEADLINE>
<P>
ALIEN DIES TRYING TO CROSS INTERSTATE 5 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An unidentified pedestrian was killed while attempting to cross the southbound 
lanes of Interstate 5 at Camp Pendleton, the coroner's office reported Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
The victim, one of a group of illegal aliens who were crossing the freeway, was 
struck by a car about 9:20 p.m. Monday about 3 miles north of Las Pulgas Road, 
authorities said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
